text: Henry Boteler (fl. 1413–1427), of Horsham, Sussex, was an English politician. ==Family== Boteler was the son of Henry Boteler, also an MP for Horsham. ==Career== He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Horsham in May 1413, March 1416, December 1421, 1422 and 1427. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:People from Horsham Category:English MPs May 1413 Category:English MPs March 1416 Category:English MPs December 1421 Category:English MPs 1422 Category:English MPs 1427
